OL,3,CStarmer in the 'endgame' of his time
OL,4,Cin office as pressure grows on him to
OL,5,Cquit
OL,7,FAll parliamentary eyes are currently
OL,8,Fon his cabinet. There is a hope among
OL,9,Fthose who want the PM to quit in a
OL,10,Fdignified and unchaotic way that they
OL,11,Fwill collectively inform him he has no
OL,12,Fchoice.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
